# ⚙️ Konfigurasi MikroTik

Reset dulu:

```bash
/system reset-configuration no-defaults=yes skip-backup=yes
```

# IP LAN (ether2)

```bash
/ip address add address=192.168.16.1/24 interface=ether2
```

# DHCP Server untuk LAN

```bash
/ip pool add name=dhcp_pool ranges=192.168.16.10-192.168.16.100
/ip dhcp-server add name=dhcp_srv interface=ether2 address-pool=dhcp_pool disabled=no
/ip dhcp-server network add address=192.168.16.0/24 gateway=192.168.16.1 dns-server=192.168.16.1
```

# WAN (ether1) → DHCP client

```bash
/ip dhcp-client add interface=ether1 disabled=no
```

# NAT masquerade

```bash
/ip firewall nat add chain=srcnat out-interface=ether1 action=masquerade
```

---

# 🔐 Firewall

```bash
/ip firewall filter add chain=input connection-state=invalid action=drop comment="Drop invalid"
/ip firewall filter add chain=input in-interface=ether2 action=accept comment="Allow LAN"
/ip firewall filter add chain=input connection-state=established,related action=accept comment="Allow established"
/ip firewall filter add chain=input action=drop comment="Drop all others"
```

---

# 🚫 Blokir detik.com

```bash
/ip dns set servers=8.8.8.8 allow-remote-requests=yes
/ip dns static add name=detik.com address=127.0.0.1
/ip dns static add name=www.detik.com address=127.0.0.1
```

---

# 💻 VPCS

```bash
ip dhcp
ping 192.168.16.1
ping 8.8.8.8
ping google.com   # harus sukses
ping detik.com    # harus gagal
```

---

# 🐧 Kali Linux

DHCP:

```bash
sudo dhclient eth0
```

Kalau DHCP gagal → manual:

```bash
sudo ip addr add 192.168.16.20/24 dev eth0
sudo ip route add default via 192.168.16.1
echo "nameserver 192.168.16.1" | sudo tee /etc/resolv.conf
```

---

# 🛠️ Troubleshooting

1. **Cek interface & IP**

   ```bash
   ip addr show
   ```

2. **Flush IP dobel**

   ```bash
   sudo ip addr flush dev eth0
   ```

3. **Perbaiki route default**

   ```bash
   sudo ip route add default via 192.168.16.1
   ```

4. **DNS error (ping IP bisa, ping domain gagal)**

   ```bash
   echo "nameserver 192.168.16.1" | sudo tee /etc/resolv.conf
   ```

5. **Kalau detik.com masih bisa → flush DNS cache client**

   ```bash
   sudo systemd-resolve --flush-caches
   ```
